&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://vvwwv.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/buuctf/%7BUY%24VMNCNP1QOQQ%40%5B%24N%24LHG.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
